- DoubleJudge findings combine: order tags '[A-first]'/'[B-first]' present, both passes included.
- DoubleJudge error propagation: a queued-stub that errors on the 2nd call -> Evaluate returns that err (no degrade); coherence failure on 2nd response -> ErrJudgeOutputInvalid.
